sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Người dùng
    participant FE as Giao diện Focus
    participant Ctrl as FocusSessionController
    participant Repo as FocusSessionRepository
    participant DB as SQL Server

    U->>FE: Chọn thời lượng focus
    FE->>Ctrl: POST /api/FocusSession/start
    Ctrl->>Repo: AddAsync(FocusSession)
    Repo->>DB: Insert session
    DB-->>Repo: session created
    Ctrl-->>FE: FocusSessionResponseDto
    FE-->>U: Bắt đầu đếm giờ

    U->>FE: Kết thúc focus session
    FE->>Ctrl: PUT /api/FocusSession/{id}/end
    Ctrl->>Repo: GetByIdAsync(id)
    Repo->>DB: Load session
    DB-->>Repo: session data
    alt Session không tồn tại hoặc sai owner
        Ctrl-->>FE: 404 / 403
    else Hợp lệ
        Ctrl->>Repo: Update EndedAt, BreaksTaken, IsCompleted
        Repo->>DB: SaveChanges
        DB-->>Repo: updated session
        Ctrl-->>FE: FocusSessionResponseDto
        FE->>Ctrl: GET /api/FocusSession/stats
        Ctrl->>Repo: GetByUserIdAndDateAsync / RangeAsync
        Repo->>DB: Query statistics
        DB-->>Repo: stats data
        Ctrl-->>FE: FocusStatsDto
    end
